Half of 18 cows is 9. When we say "5 more than half," we add 5 to this half:<tool_call>
{
    "name": math_eval,
    "arguments": {"expr": "9 + 5"},
}
</tool_call>
<tool_result>
{
    "name": math_eval,
    "arguments": {"expr": "9 + 5"},
    "result": 14,
}
</tool_result>

This gives us 14 black cows. Therefore, the non-black cows must be:<tool_call>
{
    "name": math_eval,
    "arguments": {"expr": "18 - 14"},
}
</tool_call>
<tool_result>
{
    "name": math_eval,
    "arguments": {"expr": "18 - 14"},
    "result": 4,
